# NexusFlow Build Summary Template

Use this file as a template for human-written build or release summaries.

## Repository Snapshot

- Branch: `<branch-name>`
- Commit: `<sha>`
- Scope validated: `<rust | typescript | jwt-lab | full>`

## Checks Run

- `make fmt-check`
- `make lint`
- `make test`
- `make smoke-jwt-lab`

Remove any command that was not actually run.

## What Changed

- `<brief, factual summary of the change>`
- `<second summary if needed>`

## Known Limits

- Do not claim services, chapters, or integrations are complete unless they are
  present in the repository and validated.
- Call out any skipped checks explicitly.
- Mark demo or prototype behavior clearly.
